  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Step 1: Login to shopify admin. \u00a0Go to Online Store.</strong></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936949314/image-20230608-180542.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p><strong>Step 2: Go to Themes</strong></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936949314/image-20230608-180547.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p><strong>Step 3: Click on the \u2018\u2026\u2019 next to Customize Theme and choose Edit HTML/CSS.</strong></p><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936949314/Shopify+-+Setup+Liquid+Template+for+suppliers?preview=%2F1936949314%2F1985118291%2FInvalid+file+id+-+4baf6127-16b1-4f62-b5e8-b3a5d02d52aa\"><span style=\"background: url('/wiki/s/-640127513/6452/0000891dee48b240c5ed2f93f8ac8ad513a32a09/1000.0.0-0000891dee48/_/download/resources/com.atlassian.confluence.plugins.confluence-view-file-macro:view-file-macro-resources/images/placeholder-medium-file.png'); width: 250px; height: 95px; display: inline-block; padding-top: 155px; margin: 2px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-align: center; vertical-align: text-bottom; text-decoration: none; font-size: 12px; color: #000;\">Invalid file id - 4baf61\u2026</span></a><p /><p><strong>Step 4: Click \u201cAdd a new template&quot;</strong></p><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936949314/Shopify+-+Setup+Liquid+Template+for+suppliers?preview=%2F1936949314%2F1985282113%2FInvalid+file+id+-+abdf8b44-4e12-4591-864c-5be07406e407\"><span style=\"background: url('/wiki/s/-640127513/6452/0000891dee48b240c5ed2f93f8ac8ad513a32a09/1000.0.0-0000891dee48/_/download/resources/com.atlassian.confluence.plugins.confluence-view-file-macro:view-file-macro-resources/images/placeholder-medium-file.png'); width: 250px; height: 95px; display: inline-block; padding-top: 155px; margin: 2px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-align: center; vertical-align: text-bottom; text-decoration: none; font-size: 12px; color: #000;\">Invalid file id - abdf8b\u2026</span></a><p /><p><strong>Step 5: Select \u201csearch\u201d and call it \u201cjson\u201d</strong></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936949314/image-20230608-180602.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p><strong>Step 6: Select the newly created template. \u00a0Erase the default code from your newly created template. \u00a0Then copy/paste the code below. \u00a0Then click Save.</strong></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936949314/image-20230608-180609.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>{%- layout none -%}</p><p>{%- paginate search.results by 250 -%}</p><p>{%- if search.performed -%}</p><p>{&quot;products&quot;: [</p><p>{%- for item in search.results -%}</p><p>{%- unless item.object_type == 'product' -%}{%- continue -%}{%- endunless -%}</p><p>{{- item | json -}}</p><p>{%- unless forloop.last %},{% endunless -%}</p><p>{%- endfor -%}</p><p>]}</p><p>{%- endif -%}</p><p>{%- endpaginate -%}</p><p />",
